nse disk that can form spiral arms, and then adding lower density halo and\ndisk material over time. Bars that form early in such small, dense, gas-rich\ndisks should disperse more quickly than bars that form later in fully developed\ndisks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2005 02:34:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
