etermined with the wavelet\ntransform is pointed out\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Oct 2005 16:59:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Dec 2005 20:40:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
